git project-subtree pull --squash -P vim/bundle/syntastic https://github.com/scrooloose/syntastic.git master
git project-subtree pull --squash -P vim/bundle/ctrlp https://github.com/kien/ctrlp.vim.git master
git project-subtree pull --squash -P vim/bundle/tagbar https://github.com/majutsushi/tagbar.git master
git project-subtree pull --squash -P vim/bundle/vim-airline https://github.com/bling/vim-airline.git master
git project-subtree pull --squash -P vim/bundle/vim-easymotion https://github.com/Lokaltog/vim-easymotion.git master
git project-subtree pull --squash -P vim/bundle/vim-fugitive https://github.com/tpope/vim-fugitive.git master
git project-subtree pull --squash -P vim/bundle/delimitMate https://github.com/Raimondi/delimitMate.git master
git project-subtree pull --squash -P vim/bundle/tabular https://github.com/godlygeek/tabular.git master
git project-subtree pull --squash -P vim/bundle/vim-argwrap https://github.com/FooSoft/vim-argwrap.git master


For example, to add new ones:

git project-subtree add --squash --prefix=vim/bundle/vim-fugitive https://github.com/tpope/vim-fugitive.git master

And add to the above list
